{"tid":858171,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"［未來世一登基］麥巴比登上《時代周刊》封面，並被評價為“足球的未來”","createTime":"2018-10-11T15:09:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T04:58:22.000Z","uid":31744,"like":73,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"5d45b71e57b6e5e3ac90ce5851740b0c7659f335","tid":858171,"uid":31744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:09:08.000Z","msg":"《時代周刊》這樣評價麥巴比：&ldquo;麥巴比是足球的未來，他在短短幾個月裡，憑藉自身高超的球技，被推向了國際的舞台。上年夏天，麥巴比成為了國際超級球星。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;對法國人來說，麥巴比已經不僅僅是一名無與倫比的足球運動員：他是在社會中上升並崛起的童話故事的化身。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n在《時代周刊》的採訪中，麥巴比提及了自己&ldquo;尊重、謙卑和清醒&rdquo;的價值觀。<br />\n<br />\nBY WING<br />\n記得SET埋「搶先看」，咁先唔會錯過每一個POST！ ⚽<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/11/230847_611ffd4225a184b20031d9614309a0eb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F11%2F230847_611ffd4225a184b20031d9614309a0eb.png&h=da6293bd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e69f4fae827a51d57d3964833e74dbe7b4806cc8","tid":858171,"uid":28599,"like":73,"dislike":0,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:10:39.000Z","msg":"忍者龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae743804519417f9f10402e49569564176f200ba","tid":858171,"uid":141543,"like":85,"dislike":1,"score":84,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:12:18.000Z","msg":"fifa等左咁耐終於搵到人比佢地造星了，牙朗小花之後都後繼無人"},{"pid":"2fe46b78bbf2f85d2f8346834a174cf76d6a767e","tid":858171,"uid":124983,"like":5,"dislike":5,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:15:44.000Z","msg":"垃圾"},{"pid":"e15efe8416ab99736c97f07146249f31473cdf56","tid":858171,"uid":147950,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-11T15:17:11.000Z","msg":"屁馬位置不保了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"936c25f436bf54b05877d46bab91dbb3fb7f93f4","tid":858171,"uid":4574,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"r